criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Meet DSM 5 criteria for BPD

          -  Able to provide informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  lifetime diagnosis of schizophrenia, schizoaffective disorder, bipolar disorder,
             organic mental syndromes;

          -  active substance abuse or dependence in the 6 months before the enrolment;

          -  concurrent psychotherapy;

          -  cognitive impairment or dementia;

          -  relevant neurological signs;

          -  pregnancy/lactating.
